---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>404 - 页面未找到</title>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-zinc-950 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div
        class="absolute -top-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500/20 blur-3xl rounded-full"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute top-1/3 right-0 w-125 h-125 bg-blue-500/10 blur-3xl rounded-full"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <main class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-md">
        <div
          class="text-[120px] font-black tracking-tighter text-white/10 leading-none"
        >
          404
        </div>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">
          页面已脱离当前象限
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          你访问的页面可能已经消失在时间裂缝中，<br />
          或者从未真正存在。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
          <a
            href="/"
            class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 h-11 rounded-full
                   bg-linear-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-500
                   text-white font-medium shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/20
                   transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-purple-500/40 active:scale-95"
          >
            返回安全星系

            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">
              →
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-white/30">Error Code: SPACE-404</div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
